OL,3,C2,000 British Steel jobs at risk amid
OL,4,Cplans to close Scunthorpe blast
OL,5,Cfurnaces
OL,7,FBritish Steel will close down the
OL,8,Fblast furnaces at its Scunthorpe
OL,9,Fplant in a move that unions say could
OL,10,Fcost up to 2,000 jobs.
OL,12,FThe Chinese-owned company confirmed
OL,13,Fthat it planned to replace them with
OL,14,Ftwo electric arc versions which can
OL,15,Frun on zero-carbon electricity, if it
OL,16,Fgets "appropriate support from the UK
OL,17,FGovernment".
OL,19,FIt would build one new electric arc
OL,20,Ffurnace in Scunthorpe and another at
OL,21,Fits Teesside plant.
